:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">1. 레후 - 크라운 - 수니스</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><img src=\"https://dcimg1.dcinside.com/viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce882fa1bd62531c0a64993133e134c29906eed9892027c8a6f64bb0ada2d6c03a9c12e843260f3b9b2f6ece5cfe82dad57e1bdad235171\" style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\" alt=\"viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce882fa1bd62531c0a64993133e134c29906eed9892027c8a6f64bb0ada2d6c03a9c12e843260f3b9b2f6ece5cfe82dad57e1bdad235171\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">이 부분 근처로 빠르게 버충</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><img src=\"https://dcimg1.dcinside.com/viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce882fa1bd62531c0a64993133e134c29906eed9892027c8a6f64bb0ada2d6c03a9c12e843260f3b9b2f6ecb1cdb673ff51b4b2ad235171\" style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\" alt=\"viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce882fa1bd62531c0a64993133e134c29906eed9892027c8a6f64bb0ada2d6c03a9c12e843260f3b9b2f6ecb1cdb673ff51b4b2ad235171\"></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">레후로 톡톡이 하면서 이&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">엄폐물과 뒤로 지나가는 잡몹 잡기</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">- 보스 나올때 저&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">엄폐물 뒤로 나와서</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">&nbsp;미리 부숴야함</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">잡몹을 7마리 이상 죽이면 아가리가 나오는데 바로&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(243,121,52);font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">세이렌으로 기절</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">&nbsp;걸면 다음 버스트 쓰기 가능</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">- 세이렌 기절 타이밍은 세이렌 공격 횟수에 따라 달라질 수 있음</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">아가리만 조준해놓으면 수니스 2스가 옆에 터지는 랩쳐들 자동으로 죽임</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">2. 레후 - 크라운 - 신데렐라</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">크라운 조작으로 아가리 조준하면서&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">20스택 안되게 쐈다 안쐈다 하기</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">- 안하면 공중 랩처에게 의문사 당할 수 있음</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">보통 첫 아가리 죽이고 다음 아가리 기절 걸면서 침묵 랩처는 지나가면서 잡히고 해서</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">신데 버스트안에 2마리가 다 잡힘</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">- 만약 안잡히면 잡몹을 먼저 노리고 적당한 타이밍에 기절 걸 것</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">공중 랩처가 쏠려 할때 20스택 만들기</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">3. 세이렌 - 크라운 - 수니스</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">공중 랩처 6마리 제거 -&gt; 엘리트 피 최대한 깎기</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">죽이면 안됨</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">크라운 대략 11~13스택</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(243,121,52);font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">세이렌</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">&nbsp;- 크라운 - 신데렐라</span></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">딸피 잡는데 레후 쓸 필요가 없고 수니스로 보스 옆에 떨어지는 터지는 랩처를 잡아야 돼서 레후를 아낌</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><img src=\"https://dcimg1.dcinside.com/viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce882fa1bd62531c0a64993133e134c29906eed9892027c8a6f64bb0ada2d6c03a9c12e843260f3b9b2f6ecb19ce82aa307b3ebad235171\" style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:'맑은 고딕';font-size:12px;\" alt=\"viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce882fa1bd62531c0a64993133e134c29906eed9892027c8a6f64bb0ada2d6c03a9c12e843260f3b9b2f6ecb19ce82aa307b3ebad235171\"></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">아가리 머리 조준</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">- 코어 조준 하면&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">잡몹 잡혀서</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">&nbsp;보스 나옴</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">풀버 끝날때&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(243,121,52);font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">크라운 18스택</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">&nbsp;정도면 밑의 따발총 쏘는 랩처 공격 무적</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">5. 레후 - 크라운 - 수니스</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">이제는 코어 조준해서 죽이기</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">1~2마리 뿜고 죽는데 뿜어져 나온 침묵 랩처 빠르게 제거</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">보스가 나오는데&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">보스 먼저 기절</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">걸고 옆에 터지는 랩처 잡기</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">- 빠르게 기절 걸어야 다음 신데 버스트때&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">침묵 랩처를 잡을 시간이 생김</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">6. 세이렌 - 크라운 - 신데렐라</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">잡몹을 어느정도 제거 하고</span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">침묵 랩처 나오면 우선 제거</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(209,72,65);font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\"><br></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-weight:700;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">7. 레후 - 크라운 - 수니스</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height:1.4;color:rgb(65,65,65);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:'맑은 고딕';\">맨 앞에 터지는 랩처 잡고 보스 점사하면 클리어</span></p>",
